    <ThingDef ParentName="CVN_BP_ArmorBase">
        <defName>BP_DBArmorA</defName>
        <label>Death spiked carapace</label>
        <description>Specially forged suits of carapace armor, reserved solely for members of the Death Brigade. Carapace Armour consists of large, rigid plates of ceramite, molded to fit parts of the body. Carapace Armour is stronger and thicker than the Flak Armour.\n\n This particular design features a single spiked shoulder pad and reinforcements made of rebar on the back.</description>
