	<ThingDef ParentName="CVN_BP_ArmorBase">
        <defName>BP_Goremagesuit</defName>
        <label>Gore Mage cuirass</label>
        <description>The armor of a Gore Mage, a Chaos Psyker of the Blood Pact. \n\nGore Mages are spellcasters of Khorne, based heavily in the beliefs of the ancient cults from which the Pact descends. Khornate psykers are quite rare due to Khorne's hatred of magic, so equipment for them tends to be scarce among his followers - this makes Gore Mage apparel fairly crude and heavily armored to encourage them to remain on the frontlines.</description>
        <recipeMaker>
